BOOLEAN PhoneNumberMatchRule::ExecuteRule (  const DataItem &  dataitem  )  [virtual]
 

ExecuteRule Expects a DataItem of PhoneNumberType does the actual comparision between the PhoneNumber given in the argument and the PhoneNumber stored when the PhoneNumberMatchRule was constructed. Comparison is done by calling PhoneNumber::IsMatching
